propvalues_json.sql:
SELECT 
    sourceSystem,
    eqid,
    start,
    finish,
    operationCode,
    operationName,
    withoutClient,
    login,
    branchEQNumber,
    positionName,
    positionCode,
    gangName,
    timeOpen,
    timeClose,
    isEmployee,
    isAClub,
    clientSessionId,
    operationType,
    prClientSession,
    segmentCode,
    fio,
    branchEQNumberTransfer,
    positionNameTransfer,
    branchEQMnemonic,
    branchEQMnemonicTransfer,
    employeeOfficeCode,
    officeCode,
    isOOP,
    sourceOperationId,
    isBranchRB,
    Profit_Center_Rus,
    ukd,
    insertDate,
    serviceIn,
	snapshotInsertDate
FROM
 ors.KSM1TransferSnapshot 
WHERE
 snapshotInsertDate >= CAST('$$P_START_STAMP' AS DATETIME)  and
snapshotInsertDate < CAST('$$P_END_STAMP' AS DATETIME)
AND start >= DATEADD(MONTH, -1, DATEFROMPARTS(YEAR(GETDATE()-1), MONTH(GETDATE()-1), 1))
AND start <= CAST(GETDATE()-1 AS DATE);
